<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_ef813c70-58f6-4bc8-8b00-04623662fa3f" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NT"><sptc>H6D2</sptc><title id="_30e45904-1d69-41f0-9103-b2e02e2d1c4a">Application of Part H6</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_9d7086f7-347f-4ec4-8a39-0f6dce480ef0" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_93423e3f-65b4-4359-a819-9e1da480e4fc">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1395_4.0.0.xml#_1701cd31-3169-47c9-b8fd-604c5091183b" id="_5040e797-70f0-4eea-8e95-cd5faa11edf8" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">Performance Requirement</xref> <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/7652_0.5.0.xml#_5ee6e82d-1a8d-4a31-ab67-16547aa4a9d0" id="_a932eb35-7b73-4711-a3a9-152a4ba5e0f4" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">NT H6P1</xref> for the thermal performance of the building is satisfied by— </p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e25cf04f-9b86-42e8-8e32-b263acaf7f26">a building must achieve an energy rating, using <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1342_0.23.0.xml#_6c55de1e-1960-4288-9039-42ff351adde3" id="_286ec5d2-0152-40be-b0d7-4449d8faf59e" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">house energy rating software</xref>, of greater than or equal to 5 stars; or </li><li id="_a69e2bba-77f0-4de1-b0cc-281ddffa3cc7">complying with the following parts of the ABCB Housing Provisions—<ol outputclass="numbered"><li><xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/7718#_8debb301-04f6-4af8-a595-4b97fa0cbfc4" id="_991a4496-1b1b-49e7-a926-16ab9a7596c2" publishing-id="housing" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="standard-part">NT Part 13.2</xref> for the building <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1269_0.5.0.xml#_9470eb17-f8ba-4a37-9a7e-a343418f0ac7" id="_6de962ce-f191-4c2c-9cb8-ef904e372c82" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">fabric</xref>; and </li><li><xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/7719#_99a96a13-5758-4375-9b53-40b7538e2159" id="_2c8140ef-f1e1-4d14-a309-0a428651a70b" publishing-id="housing" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="standard-part">NT Part 13.3</xref> for the external <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1319_2.9.0.xml#_9067b5ce-fa3e-4afd-9b3a-b3520543cb5d" id="_41896b34-1213-48e5-bf54-a154e035763c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">glazing</xref> and shading; and</li><li><xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/7725#_a7f2480c-ca32-4e7d-a7d6-6b6087d7efb7" id="_2fcf780f-fde4-4f44-be97-fd213d0e83b3" publishing-id="housing" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="standard-part">NT Part 13.4</xref> for building sealing; and </li><li><xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/7726#_93755729-db2b-4eee-ac2d-d8bda79f91cb" id="_535cbdda-75a5-496c-a118-b3641e4a9e0f" publishing-id="housing" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="standard-part">NT Part 13.5</xref> for air movement.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_f4a40753-3b3e-4f06-88a6-5590ea71a826" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ea61e50c-d493-4d36-a3e5-c73eb862cc33">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" xmlns:qxa="urn:schemas-quark-com:xmlauthor" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1395_4.0.0.xml#_1701cd31-3169-47c9-b8fd-604c5091183b" id="_5590ed41-d56a-4d0c-a583-79fba56c7923" inv:access="external" qxa:read-only="true" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="true" type="glossterm">Performance Requirement</xref> <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/7654_0.4.0.xml#_73f0922c-f353-4ba9-9f16-ae19844e390f" id="_7a9eb1b4-eaae-4010-8e47-3da6e9a8077e" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">NT H6P2</xref> for the energy usage of a building is satisfied by – </p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_050ae75d-790b-4ee2-9b9c-b7f07906b37a">a building must achieve an energy rating, using <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1342_0.23.0.xml#_6c55de1e-1960-4288-9039-42ff351adde3" id="_0cb162cb-1427-43c3-a57f-fd61fc76200b" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">house energy rating software</xref>, of greater than or equal to 5 stars; or</li><li id="_547bec20-b86f-47cf-adc5-57acba485b2b">complying with <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/7727#_37280217-f0fb-475d-9f27-10d84bdd909a" id="_0fdc0e35-4920-4430-9652-b1e9d4c42d40" publishing-id="housing" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="standard-part">NT Part 13.6</xref> of the ABCB Housing Provisions for services.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_f94d55b2-073c-4df8-908b-61ad90145536"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>There are two options for complying with the energy efficiency <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1395_4.0.0.xml#_1701cd31-3169-47c9-b8fd-604c5091183b" id="_3e6e97a5-f56b-453c-bfc1-7b34b85327c8" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">Performance Requirements</xref>:</p><ul><li>Option 1 Energy rating – achieving the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1432_4.0.0.xml#_a5b45a91-1ac3-44a8-8644-acfc09c225a9" id="_a1b35812-9a6e-4b3b-b6c6-e58ef9e4f039" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">required</xref> energy rating.</li><li>Option 2 Elemental Provisions – satisfy all the detailed provisions including meeting the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1490_25.4.0.xml#_5a8cb42e-a549-40fa-a685-3422c624c5b7" id="_e91d9796-28a6-418c-8f37-d0d3087b41b0" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">Total R-Values</xref> of roofs, walls and floors, the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1319_2.9.0.xml#_9067b5ce-fa3e-4afd-9b3a-b3520543cb5d" id="_50234253-5196-46e3-8cdd-b3e728048e8d" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">glazing</xref> allowances and the air movement requirements.</li></ul></callout></clause>